    },
    {
      "ChoiceID": 1064,
      "Name": "11280236859052038662",
      "Text": "校长办公室中几乎没有任何与花草茶相关的东西。",
      "IsShow": {
        "$arrayRef": 1468
      },
      "RightChoiceID1": 1066,
      "Plotgame1": 16209784,
      "RightChoiceID2": 0,
      "Plotgame2": 0,
      "RightChoiceID3": 0,
      "Plotgame3": 0
    },
    {
      "ChoiceID": 1065,
      "Name": "5331069146986795626",
      "Text": "校长曾为了维护花草茶事件，与佐尔娅争论。",
      "IsShow": {
        "$arrayRef": 1468
      },
      "RightChoiceID1": 1067,
      "Plotgame1": 16209788,
      "RightChoiceID2": 0,
      "Plotgame2": 0,
      "RightChoiceID3": 0,
      "Plotgame3": 0
    },
    {
      "ChoiceID": 1066,
      "Name": "18249994672769877600",
      "Text": "校长很少喝花草茶。或许是因为空闲时间不够，或许单纯没有找到合适的口味。",
      "IsShow": {
        "$arrayRef": 1468
